{"word":"συντρίβω","slug":"συντρίβω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συντρίβω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, τρίβω</el> ‘rub’] ‘to alter the condition of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> through force’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> break</b> a plant growth <b><a href='B:470 12:20'>Mt 12:20</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el>ϰατεάγω</el> break off); a binding device <b><a href='B:480 5:4'>Mk 5:4</a>;</b> the seal on a jar <b>14:3;</b> a bone <b><a href='B:500 19:36'>J 19:36</a>;</b> pottery <b><a href='B:730 2:27'>Rv 2:27</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> hurt</b> a human body <b><a href='B:490 9:39'>Lk 9:39</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> crush <a href='B:520 16:20'>Ro 16:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συντρέχω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σύντριμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}